latestPosts.caption:
Five years ago, when I started posting makeup tutorials on this platform, I faced immense hate and trolling. People mocked my skin tone, calling me ‘kali’ and ‘ugly’. But I didn’t let their negativity bring me down. Instead, I used it as fuel to drive my passion for makeup.

As a girl with zero knowledge about makeup, I learned everything from YouTube videos. And today, I stand before you, proud to have won the Best Beauty Influencer of the Year award.

This moment isn’t just a victory for me; it’s a testament to the power of perseverance and self-love. To everyone who has ever faced hate or bullying, I see you, I hear you, and I believe in you.

Thank you to my family, friends, and my audience for their unwavering support, thank you for embracing me and my content. This award is for all of us, and I’m honoured to share it with each and every one of you.

And Ofcourse, Mahadev ko kese bhul sakti hu🥹🙏

Btw wearing this beautiful piece from @niyara_india ✨
